quran[49]{c,v,t}:
  43,57,"Aur jonhi ke ibne Maryam (Jesus) ki misal di gayi, tumhari qaum ke logon ne uspar gul macha diya (chilla utthey/ raised a clamour)"
  43,58,"Aur lagey kehne ke hamare maabood acche hain ya woh? Yeh misaal woh tumhare saamne mehaz kach-behasi (argument/ contentiousness) ke liye laaye hain, haqeeat yeh hai ke yeh hain hi jhagdalu log"
  43,59,Ibne Maryam (Jesus) iske siwa kuch na tha ek banda tha jispar humne inaam kiya aur bani israel ke liye apni qudrat ka ek namuna bana diya
  43,60,Hum chahein to tumse farishte paida kardein jo zameen mein tumhare janasheen(successors) hon
  43,61,"Aur woh dar-asal qayamat ki ek nishani hai, pas tum usmein shakk na karo meri baat maan lo, yahi seedha raasta hai"
  43,62,Aisa na ho shaytan tumko ussey roak de ke woh tumhara khula dushman hai
  43,63,"Aur jab Isa (Jesus) sareeh nishaniyan liye huey aaya tha to usne kaha tha ke “main tum logon ke paas hikmat lekar aaya hoon, aur isliye aaya hoon ke tumpar baaz un baaton ki haqeeqat khol doon jin mein tum ikhtilaf kar rahey ho, lihaza tum Allah se daro aur meri itaat karo"
  43,64,"Haqeeqat yeh hai ke Allah hi mera Rubb bhi hai aur tumhara Rubb bhi.Usi ki tum ibadat karo, yahi seedha raasta hai”"
  43,65,"Magar (uski is saaf taleem ke bawajood) girohon (factions) ne aapas mein ikhtilaf kiya, pas tabahi hai un logon ke liye jinhon ne zulm kiya ek dardnaak din ke azaab se"
  43,66,Kya yeh log ab bas isi cheez ke muntazir hain ke achanak inpar qiyamat aa jaye aur inhein khabar bhi na ho
  43,67,Woh din jab aayega to muttaqin ko chodh kar baaki sab dost ek dursre ke dushman ho jayenge
  43,68,Us roz un logon se jo hamari aayat par imaan laaye thay aur mutii-e-farmaan bankar rahey thay
  43,69,"Kaha jayega ke “aey mere bandon (servents), aaj tumhare liye koi khauff nahin aur na tumhein koi gham lahiq hoga"
  43,70,"Dakhil ho jao jannat mein tum aur tumhari biwiyan, tumhein khush kardiya jaayega”"
  43,71,"Unke aagay soonay (golden) ke thal (Platters) aur sagar gardish karaye jayenge aur har mann bhaati aur nigaahon ko lazzat dene wali cheez wahan maujood hogi. Unse kaha jayega, “tum ab yahan hamesha rahoge"
  43,72,Tum is jannat ke waaris apne un aamal ki wajah se huey ho jo tum duniya mein karte rahe
  43,73,Tumhare liye yahan bakasrat fawake(abundant fruits) maujood hain jinhein tum khaogey”
  43,74,"Rahe mujreem , to woh hamesha jahannum ke azaab mein mubtala rahenge"
  43,75,"Kabhi unke azaab mein kami na hogi, aur woh us mein mayous padey hongey"
  43,76,Unpar humne zulm nahin kiya balke woh khud hi apne upar zulm karte rahey
  43,77,"Woh pukarenge, “aey maalik, tera Rubb hamara kaam hi tamam ka de to accha hai” woh jawab dega “tum yun hi padey rahogey"
  43,78,Hum tumhare paas haqq lekar aaye thay magar tum mein se aksar ko haqq hi nagawaar tha”
  43,79,Kya in logon ne koi iqdam (plot) karne ka faisla karliya hai? Accha to hum bhi phir ek faisla kiye letey hain
  43,80,Kya inhon ne yeh samajh rakkha hai ke hum inki raaz ki baatein aur inki sargoshiyan sunte nahin hain? Hum sab kuch sun rahey hain aur hamare farishtey inke paas hi likh rahe hain
  43,81,"Inse kaho, agar waqai Rehman ki koi aulad hoti to sabse pehle Ibadat karne wala main hota”"
  43,82,"Paak hai aasmaano aur zameen ka farma rawan, Arsh ka maalik, un saari baaton se jo yeh log us ki taraf mansoob karte hain"
  43,83,"Accha, inhein apne baatil khayalat mein garq aur apne khel mein munhamik rehne do, yahan tak ke yeh apna woh din dekh lein jiska inhein khauff dilaya jaa raha hai"
  43,84,"Wahi ek aasman mein bhi khuda hai aur zameen mein bhi khuda, aur wahi hakeem o Aleem hai"
  43,85,"Bahut baala-o-bartar hai woh jiske qabze mein zameen aur aasmaano aur har us cheez ki baadshahi hai jo zameen o aasman ke darmiyan payi jaati hai. Aur wahi qayamat ki ghadi ka ilm rakhta hai, aur usi ki taraf tum sab paltaye jaane waale ho"
  43,86,"Usko chodh kar yeh log jinhein pukarte hain woh kisi shafaat ka ikhtiyar nahin rakhte, illa yeh ke koi ilm ki bina par haqq ki shahadat de"
  43,87,Aur agar tum insey pucho ke inhein kisne paida kiya hai to yeh khud kahenge ke Allah ne. Phir kahan se yeh dhoka kha rahe hain
  43,88,"Kasam hai Rasool ke is qaul ki ke aey Rubb, yeh woh log hain jo maan kar nahin detay"
  43,89,"Accha, aey nabi insey darguzar karo aur kehdo ke salaam hai tumhein, anqareeb inhein maaloom ho jayega"
  44,1,Haa Meem
  44,2,Kasam hai is kitaab e Mubeen ki
  44,3,"Ke humne isey ek badi khair o barakat wali raat mein nazil kiya hai, kyunke hum logon ko mutanabbeh (warning) karne ka irada rakhte thay"
  44,4,Yeh woh raat thi jismein har maamle ka hakeemana faisla
  44,5,Hamare hukum se sadir kiya jata hai. Hum ek Rasool bhejne waley thay
  44,6,Tere Rubb ki rehmat ke taur par.Yaqeenan wahi sab kuch sunne aur jaanne wala hai
  44,7,Aasmano aur zameen ka Rubb aur har us cheez ka Rubb jo Aasman o zameen ke darmiyan hai agar tum log waqaii yakeen rakhne waley ho
  44,8,Koi maabood uske siwa nahin hai. Wahi zindagi ata karta hai aur wahi maut deta hai.Tumhara Rubb aur tumhare un aslaaf (forefathers) ka Rubb jo pehle guzar chuke hain
  44,9,(Magar fil-waqeh in logon ko yaqeen nahin hai) balke yeh apne shakk mein paday khel rahey hain
  44,10,Accha intezar karo us din ka jab aasman sareeh dhuwan (smoke) liye huey aayega
  44,11,"Aur woh logon par chaa jayega, yeh hai dardnaak saza"
  44,12,"(Ab kehte hain ke) “ parwardigar , humpar se yeh azaab taal de, hum imaan laatey hain”"
  44,13,Inki gaflat kahan dur hoti hai? Inka haal to yeh hai ke in ke paas Rasool e mubeen aa gaya
  44,14,Phir bhi yeh uski taraf multafit na huey aur kaha ke “ yeh to sikhaya padaya bawla hai (well-tutored madman)”
  44,15,"Hum zara azaab hataye detay hain, tum log phir wahi kuch karoge jo pehle kar rahe thay"
  44,16,Jis roz hum badi zarb (assault) lagayenge woh din hoga jab hum tumse intiqaam lenge